{"tid":2271772,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如果拜登真係270票 選舉人團唔投佢咁點","createTime":"2020-11-04T17:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T17:50:56.000Z","uid":44218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ff16e5c6f939116fe6559313a927da12052af3d7","tid":2271772,"uid":44218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T17:28:07.000Z","msg":"好似威斯康星州咁無啦啦多左禁多票出黎<br />\n選舉人好唔gur 咁唔投佢<br />\n咁少左一票既拜登仲當唔當選到？<br />\n<br />\n<em>失信選舉人，又譯作不忠選舉人（英文：Faithless elector）指美國選舉人團中，沒有將票投給自己宣誓支持的總統或副總統候選人的選舉人。嚴格地說，失信選舉人與未宣誓選舉人（Unpledged elector）並不相同。</em>"},{"pid":"1a25b0e49477b99fc90ef3c368083942b905265a","tid":2271772,"uid":44218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T17:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb4d3cba755da573f5de2d1807d5772ef5e1991","tid":2271772,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T17:50:56.000Z","msg":"少一票都當選唔到<br />\n由眾議院選舉總統"}]}